  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help Families with Nodding Syndrome in N Uganda</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To help provide a better life for children and families. To help children suffer less from the symptoms of Nodding Syndrome. We will provide psychosocial support and access to medical care which will restore dignity and hope to these children and their families. We will provide nutrition and play which will reduce stigma through education and support for the families affected. The region has experienced trauma and cultural disintegration over decades of war and neglect.</narrative>
  </description>
